FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: the DOM instance id of the instance that the resource was created from

FieldDescriptors.Name: Error script
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Name of automation script to execute when error occurs in managing the resource in Resource Studio

FieldDescriptors.Name: Externally managed

FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Script which will be triggered when the current resource is being booked. This allows to include related resources into the same booking based on predefined relations or custom logic.

FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: link resource to input virtual signal groups that can be used to setup connections to the resource

FieldDescriptors.Name: output vSGs

FieldDescriptors.Name: Allow bookings on pool level
FieldDescriptors.Tooltip: Indicates if the pool is bookable in case it does not matter what actual resource in the pool is booked
